%3Cli%3EHome%20charging%20can%20take%20only%20a%20few%20hours%20and%20is%20healthier%20for%20your%20battery%20than%20fast%20charging.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgetting-ready-for-electric%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgetting-ready-for-electric%5C%22%3EGetting%20Ready%20for%20Electric%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20of%20guides%20and%20practical%20advice%20for%20buying%20your%20next%20EV.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFilling%20up%20a%20car%20with%20gas%20is%20second%20nature%20for%20nearly%20anyone%20with%20a%20driver's%20license.%20But%20charging%20an%20electric%20vehicle%3F%20For%20many%2C%20that's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-charging-range-improving-americans-still-dont-want-electric-cars-2024-9%5C%22%3Ea%20brand-new%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20electric%20introduces%20a%20whole%20new%20element%20of%20car%20ownership%3A%20charging.%20We%20spoke%20with%20experts%20at%20the%20automotive%20marketplace%20Cars.com%20and%20the%20charger%20installer%20Qmerit%20to%20demystify%20the%20process%20and%20learn%20best%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20charging%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20fast-charging%20station%20nearby%20or%20a%20plug%20available%20at%20your%20workplace%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20get%20by%20without%20charging%20at%20home.%20But%20Jenni%20Newman%2C%20editor%20in%20chief%20of%20Cars.com%20and%20an%20EV%20owner%20herself%2C%20argued%20that%20charging%20at%20home%20makes%20EV%20ownership%20convenient%20and%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHome%20charging%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20easy%20and%20efficient%20to%20own%20an%20EV%2C%26quot%3B%20Newman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20bottom%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20at-home%20charger%2C%20owners%20can%20recharge%20their%20cars%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%20They%20can%20plug%20them%20in%20overnight%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20wake%20up%20with%20250%20or%20300%20miles%20of%20driving%20range.%20This%20slower%20charging%20is%20also%20healthier%20for%20your%20car's%20battery%20over%20the%20long%20term%20%E2%80%94%20and%20depending%20on%20your%20utility%20rates%2C%20it%20could%20be%20much%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnergySage%20estimates%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-does-it-cost-to-charge-tesla%5C%22%3Echarging%20an%20EV%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20about%20%240.05%20per%20mile%20of%20range%20added%2C%20though%20that%20depends%20on%20things%20like%20location%2C%20electricity%20rates%2C%20and%20the%20type%20of%20EV%20charger%20used.%20DC%20fast%20chargers%2C%20like%20Superchargers%2C%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%240.60%20per%20kWh%2C%20depending%20on%20congestion.%20At%20home%2C%20kWh%20prices%20tend%20to%20be%20much%20lower%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20local%20utility%20and%20how%20it%20sources%20energy%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20do%20I%20get%20set%20up%20to%20charge%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20electric%20cars%20come%20with%20a%20Level%201%20charging%20cord.%20This%20cord%20plugs%20into%20a%20standard%20110-volt%20alternating-current%20household%20outlet%20and%20slowly%20adds%20a%20few%20miles%20of%20driving%20range%20an%20hour.%20But%20Newman%20said%20sluggish%20charging%20speeds%20may%20be%20tough%20to%20live%20with%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20even%20if%20you%20can%20plug%20in%20for%20a%20full%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20charging%20on%20a%20driveway%20outside%20a%20garage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bbebc46fcb546d2d4b39c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEV%20owners%20and%20experts%20recommend%20charging%20your%20EV%20at%20home%20for%20convenience%20and%20savings.%3Cp%3EUCG%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELevel%202%20charging%2C%20which%20she%20recommends%2C%20uses%20a%20higher-voltage%20connection%20to%20add%20more%20range%20per%20hour.%20These%20plugs%20can%20be%20found%20at%20public%20charging%20stations%2C%20and%20homeowners%20can%20install%20them%20in%20a%20garage%20or%20driveway.%20Some%20EVs%20also%20come%20with%20these%20chargers%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20Level%201%20plug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevel%202%20chargers%20can%20be%20plugged%20into%20a%20240-volt%20socket%20%E2%80%94%20like%20what%20you%20may%20use%20for%20an%20appliance%20like%20a%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20or%20hardwired%20into%20a%20home's%20electrical%20panel.%20Either%20way%2C%20Newman%20recommends%20consulting%20an%20electrician%20who%20specializes%20in%20charger%20installations%20to%20get%20a%20handle%20on%20the%20expected%20costs%20and%20work%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20set%20up%20my%20home%20for%20charging%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20home-charging%20setup%20varies%20widely.%20If%20you%20already%20have%20a%20240-volt%20outlet%20in%20a%20convenient%20spot%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20simply%20buy%20a%20charger%20and%20plug%20it%20in.%20Level%202%20chargers%20can%20cost%20%24250%20to%20%24750.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20you%20could%20need%20more%20extensive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20work.%20Ken%20Sapp%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20Qmerit%2C%20said%20most%20of%20its%20jobs%20cost%20%241%2C600%20or%20less%2C%20including%20permits%20but%20excluding%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20charger%20itself.%20Sapp%20added%20that%20projects%20involve%20tapping%20into%20an%20existing%20240-volt%20circuit%20(or%20adding%20one)%20and%20installing%20the%20charger%20or%20a%20dedicated%20outlet%20in%20a%20convenient%20location%2C%20like%20the%20wall%20of%20a%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farther%20your%20electrical%20panel%20is%20from%20where%20you'd%20like%20to%20plug%20in%2C%20the%20pricier%20installation%20will%20be%2C%20Sapp%20said.%20(Ideally%20your%20panel%20is%20on%20the%20same%20wall%20as%20your%20charger%2C%20but%20if%20wiring%20needs%20to%20be%20routed%20up%20from%20a%20basement%2C%20for%20example%2C%20things%20get%20trickier.)%20Moreover%2C%20Sapp%20said%2C%20some%20homes%20may%20need%20to%20upgrade%20their%20electrical%20panel%20to%20handle%20the%20extra%20load%20from%20charging%2C%20which%20could%20increase%20costs%20by%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20nozzle-like%20EV%20charger%20mounted%20on%20a%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bed5cb66c28600194387f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Level%202%20home%20charger%20can%20charge%20an%20EV%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%3Cp%3EChargePoint%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Cars.com%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cars.com%2Farticles%2Fwhat-it-cost-to-outfit-six-homes-with-ev-chargers-447239%2F%5C%22%3Einstalled%20home%20chargers%20for%20six%20of%20its%20car%20reviewers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20the%20costs%20varied%20widely.%20One%20installation%20totaled%20about%20%241%2C700.%20Another%20required%20a%20service%20upgrade%20and%20trenching%20to%20route%20a%20circuit%20across%20a%20yard%20to%20a%20detached%20garage%2C%20costing%20nearly%20%247%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20everything%20a%20bit%20easier%20on%20your%20wallet%2C%20you%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafdc.energy.gov%2Flaws%2F10513%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20tax%20credit%20that%20covers%2030%25%20of%20charger-installation%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20to%20%241%2C000.%20Utilities%20commonly%20offer%20rebates%20or%20special%20electricity%20rates%20for%20EV%20owners%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20choosing%20a%20charger%2C%20Sapp%20says%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20bet%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20with%20a%20model%20recommended%20by%20your%20car's%20manufacturer.%20Newman%20says%20the%20right%20charger%20depends%20on%20what%20your%20home%20can%20handle%20and%20what's%20best%20for%20your%20specific%20vehicle.%20An%20experienced%20electrician%20can%20help%20make%20that%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20experts%20in%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20OK%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20knowledgeable%20electrician%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20this%20side%20of%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-home-charging-electric-car-ev%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730317351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67110f083f2165d716e272ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-home-charging-electric-car-ev%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Installing%20a%20charger%20for%20your%20new%20electric%20car%20at%20home%20can%20be%20costly%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20the%20convenience%20and%20eventual%20savings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bzhang%40businessinsider.com%20(Benjamin%20Zhang%2CTim%20Levin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-home-charging-electric-car-ev%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nolan%20wanted%20Dimple%20to%20leave%20her%20earrings%20behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730317140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114790944%2Cim