dance's%20news%20feed%20aggregator%20app%20Toutiao.%20Zhang%20is%20not%20pictured.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FStringer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20news%20platform%20whose%20results%20were%20powered%20by%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20separate%20from%20China's%20search%20engine%20Baidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20push%20information%2C%20not%20by%20queries%2C%20by%20news%20recommendations%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-09-28%2F35-year-old-unknown-creates-the-world-s-most-valuable-startup%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20focus%20on%20news%2C%20Zhang%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-09-28%2F35-year-old-unknown-creates-the-world-s-most-valuable-startup%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg's%20Lulu%20Yilun%20Chen%20and%20Mark%20Bergen%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ByteDance%20does%20not%20have%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-will-hire-journalists-to-run-its-news-section-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejournalists%20on%20its%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20many%20other%20social%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20are%20not%20a%20news%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-09-28%2F35-year-old-unknown-creates-the-world-s-most-valuable-startup%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20more%20like%20a%20search%20business%20or%20a%20social%20media%20platform.%20We%20are%20doing%20very%20innovative%20work.%20We%20are%20not%20a%20copycat%20of%20a%20U.S.%20company%2C%20both%20in%20product%20and%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EZhang%20launched%20ByteDance's%20most%20successful%20app