on%20Wednesday%2C%20Schmidt%20said%20the%20low%20cost%20of%20automated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-wild-hornets-sting-shahed-drones-war-russia-iran-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20soon%20make%20traditional%20forms%20of%20combat%20obsolete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20an%20awful%20lot%20of%20tanks.%20Those%20tanks%20are%20largely%20useless%20now.%20A%20%245%2C000%20drone%20can%20destroy%20a%20%245%2C000%2C000%20tank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20read%20somewhere%20that%20the%20US%20had%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20tanks%20stored%20somewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BGive%20them%20away.%20Buy%20a%20drone%20instead.%20In%20fact%2C%20buy%2010%2C%20buy%2020%2C%20buy%2050%2C%20buy%20100.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20Schmidt%20has%20advised%20the%20US%20government%20and%20military%20on%20technology.%20He%20became%20chairman%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20Innovation%20Board%20in%202016%20and%20has%20chaired%20the%20US%20National%20Security%20Commission%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20working%20on%20a%20startup%20that%20builds%20AI%20attack%20drones%20to%20help%20Ukraine.%20Speaking%20at%20Stanford%20University%20in%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-white-stork-ai-drones-ukraine-war-russia-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20startup%2C%20named%20White%20Stork%2C%20was%20to%20use%20AI%20%26quot%3Bin%20complicated%2C%20powerful%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20is%20working%20on%20the%20project%20with%20former%20Udacity%20and%20Kittyhawk%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-kittyhawk-google-founder-billionaire-larry-page-flying-car-company-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESebastian%20Thrun%3C%2Fa