ation%20to%20shield%20them%20from%20emerging%20battlefield%20threats.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20drones%20have%20made%20the%20battlespace%20more%20transparent%20and%20more%20dangerous%2C%20conventional%20warfighting%20elements%20remain%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20Troops%20are%20being%20more%20cautious%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbradley-fighting-vehicles-prove-worth-ukraine-short-on-abrams-tanks-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etanks%20are%20still%20active%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20armored%20fighting%20vehicles%20have%20repeatedly%20proven%20their%20worth%2C%20and%20artillery%20continues%20to%20be%20king.%20However%2C%20as%20unmanned%20technology%20matures%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20AI%2C%20that%20could%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20more%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20You%20can%20reach%20the%20reporter%20Hugh%20Langley%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20(%2B1%20628-228-1836)%20or%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-drone-warfare-tanks-useless-russia-ukraine-ai%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730312809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67224ea69b3250dbbceb1cd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-drone-warfare-tanks-useless-russia-ukraine-ai%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eric%20Schmidt%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20on%20a%20drone%20startup%2C%20says%20the%20US%20should%20give%20away%20its%20tanks%20and%20buy%20drones%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40in