ur%20needs%2C%20think%20about%20how%20often%20you%20intend%20to%20use%20your%20mixer%20and%20where%20it%20might%20be%20kept%20or%20stored.%20If%20you%20plan%20to%20leave%20it%20out%20on%20your%20countertop%2C%20does%20it%20have%20a%20large%20footprint%3F%20Does%20it%20weigh%20too%20much%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20move%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%3F%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20bowl.%20Most%20recipes%20can%20be%20made%20in%20a%205-quart%20bowl%2C%20but%20you%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20making%20bigger%20batches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%20settings%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20speed%20settings%20on%20a%20stand%20mixer%20are%20what%20will%20give%20you%20control%20over%20the%20mixing%20process.%20Every%20stand%20mixer%20has%20a%20different%20number%20of%20speed%20settings.%20Lower%20speeds%20tackle%20folding%20and%20beating%2C%20while%20higher%20speeds%20are%20best%20for%20beating%20frosting%20and%20whipping%20whipped%20cream%20or%20egg%20whites%20for%20meringue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20construction%20of%20a%20stand%20mixer%20is%20key%20to%20its%20performance.%20Most%20stand%20mixers%20are%20made%20out%20of%20die-cast%20metal%2C%20which%20makes%20for%20a%20solid-metal%20base.%20The%20weight%20of%20this%20base%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20providing%20stability%20while%20beating%20or%20kneading.%20Many%20budget%20stand%20mixers%20are%20constructed%20from%20plastic%2C%20which%20doesn't%20offer%20as%20much%20weight.%20Consider%20the%20types%20of%20recipes%20you%20may%20be%20making%20in%20your%20stand%20mixer%20to%20determine%20the%20mixer%20constructed%20from%20the%20best%20material%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ea4d161-ef77-4144-9c9d-00ea7a4dad9c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20shot%20of%20a%20stand%20mixer%20beating%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20dough.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e71973cc84b4dfa003f9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20each%20test%2C%20I%20monitored%20the%20noise%20level%20and%20heat%20of%20the%20mixer%20motors.%3Cp%3EMolly%20Allen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%2011%20stand%20mixers%20we%20evaluated%20was%20put%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%2C%20including%20making%20a%20batch%20of%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20dough%2C%20a%20batch%20of%20pizza%20dough%2C%20and%20a%20batch%20of%20homemade%20whipped%20cream.%20This%20allowed%20us%20to%20test%20the%20mixer%20using%20the%20paddle%2C%20dough%20hook%2C%20and%20whisk%20attachments%20if%20those%20attachments%20were%20included%20in%20the%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeating%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20made%20a%20batch%20of%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20dough%20in%20each%20stand%20mixer%20using%20the%20paddle%20attachment.%20With%20this%20test%2C%20I%20assessed%20how%20well%20the%20mixer%20performed%20while%20creaming%20butter%20and%20sugar%2C%20along%20with%20how%20the%20motor%20while%20mixing%20a%20tough%20dough%20with%20chocolate%20chips%20included.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKneading%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20made%20a%20batch%20of%20pizza%20dough%20using%20the%20dough%20hook%20on%20each%20stand%20mixer.%20I%20evaluated%20each%20stand%20mixer%20based%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20knead%20the%20dough%20without%20any%20motor%20snagging%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhipping%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20poured%201%20cup%20of%20heavy%20whipping%20cream%20in%20each%20stand%20mixer%20and%20used%20the%20whisk%20attachment%20to%20make%20homemade%20whipped%20cream.%20I%20timed%20each%20mixer%20to%20see%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20perform%20this%20task%2C%20along%20with%20assessing%20for%20any%20issues%20throughout%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%20and%20capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20evaluated%20each%20stand%20mixer%20based%20on%20its%20size%20and%20how%20much%20space%20it%20took%20up%20on%20the%20countertop%2C%20along%20with%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20mixing%20bowl%20to%20perform%20each%20task.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9c8d626-b34a-443f-9254-d6538d288ab8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EFAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20power%20for%20a%20stand%20mixer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20stand%20mixer%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20the%20motor%20can%20power%20through%20most%20batters%20and%20doughs%20you're%20making.%20A%20mixer%20with%20at%20least%20300%20watts%20to%20550%20watts%20will%20have%20no%20issues%20kneading%20tough%20dough%20and%20making%20double%20batches%20of%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20hand%20mixer%20better%20than%20a%20stand%20mixer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStand%20mixers%20are%20most%20often%20constructed%20from%20metal%2C%20making%20them%20much%20heavier%20than%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-hand-mixer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20hand%20mixer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They're%20meant%20for%20countertop%20use%20and%20free%20up%20your%20hands.%20Hand%20mixers%20are%20generally%20less%20expensive%20and%20smaller%2C%20but%20need%20to%20be%20held%20throughout%20the%20mixing%20task%20and%20are%20less%20powerful.%20For%20occasional%20bakers%20or%20those%20with%20really%20limited%20space%2C%20hand%20mixers%20are%20a%20great%20choice.%20Still%2C%20if%20you%20can%20swing%20it%2C%20the%20best%20stand%20mixers%20give%20you%20more%20versatility%20and%20power.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20different%20types%20of%20stand%20mixers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20main%20types%20of%20stand%20mixers%20are%20the%20tilt-head%20and%20the%20bowl-lift.%20A%20tilt-head%20