0new%20jobs%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpectations%20for%20October's%20headline%20payrolls%20number%20are%20already%20relatively%20low%20at%20around%20110%2C000-120%2C000.%20Economists%20and%20investors%20are%20discounting%20the%20impact%20that%20Hurricanes%20Milton%20and%20Helene%20and%20the%20ongoing%20strike%20at%20Boeing%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20on%20the%20jobs%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20accounting%20for%20these%20extraordinary%20events%2C%20however%2C%20some%20experts%20say%20a%20weak%20number%20below%20that%20consensus%20could%20counter%20the%20prevailing%20narrative%20that%20rapid%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20slowed%20inflation%20without%20tipping%20the%20economy%20into%20recessionary%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20a%20so-called%20soft%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%2050%2C000%20or%20less%2C%20even%20with%20those%20potential%20disruptions%2C%20that%20does%20bring%20back%20some%20concerns%20about%20a%20slowdown%2C%26quot%3B%20Tom%20Essaye%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sevens%20Report%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20it%20really%20counters%20this%20idea%20that%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20no%20landing%2C%20that%20the%20economy's%20just%20not%20going%20to%20slow%20at%20all.%20So%20I%20think%20it%20would%20move%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20McMillan%2C%20the%20CIO%20of%20IDX%20Advisors%2C%20said%20the%20same%20about%20a%20jobs%20print%20well-below%20consensus%2C%20especially%20given%20how%20much%20investor%20sentiment%20about%20a%20soft%20landing%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20upside%20in%20the%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20a%20situation%20where%20many%20investors%20say%20to%20themselves%2C%20'Alright%2C%20maybe%20the%20economy%20is%20not%20as%20robust%20as%20we%20thought%2C'%20things%20could%20be%20more%20prone%20to%20slowing%20down%2C%20and%20therefore%20investors%20revise%20their%20risk-on%20outlook%20appropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20estimates%20that%20the%20hurricanes%20will%20lower%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%20added%20by%2040%2C000-50%2C000%2C%20meaning%20a%20potential%20jobs%20print%20of%20200%2C000%20would%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20be%20reduced%20to%20150%2C000-160%2C000.%20Pantheon%20Macroeconomics%20says%20the%20impact%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20closer%20to%2025%2C000%20jobs.%20For%20the%20strikes%20at%20Boeing%20and%20other%20firms%2C%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20itself%20estimates%20that%20they'll%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fces%2Fpublications%2Fstrike-report.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20job%20gains%20by%2044%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20various%20surveys%20of%20economists%20show%20muted%20expectations%20for%20October%2C%20some%20warn%20there's%20a%20chance%20that%20job%20gains%20could%20be%20lower%20than%20the%20110%2C000-120%2C000%20consensus.%20Goldman%20is%20just%20under%20that%20with%20a%2095%2C000%20prediction%2C%20while%20Comerica%20is%20much%20lower%20at%2030%2C000.%20Former%20Fed%20economist%20Claudia%20Sahm%20thinks%20the%20print%20could%20even%20be%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20print%20of%20under%20100%2C000%20would%20be%20the%20first%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hurricanes%20and%20strikes%2C%20however%2C%20make%20it%20unclear%20where%20the%20threshold%20of%20worry%20is%20for%20investors%20in%20a%20significant%20miss%20to%20the%20downside.%20Michael%20Cuggino%2C%20the%20president%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20of%20the%20Permanent%20Portfolio%20Family%20of%20Funds%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday%20that%20investors%20might%20be%20quick%20to%20disregard%20a%20poor%20number%20due%20to%20the%20temporary%20factors%20listed%20above.%20Plus%2C%20they%20may%20even%20cheer%20on%20the%20chance%20of%20larger%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Adams%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20at%20Comerica%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20this%20week%20that%20while%20his%20expectations%20are%20very%20low%2C%20investors%20shouldn't%20jump%20to%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20October%20jobs%20report%20will%20likely%20show%20a%20severe%20but%20short-lived%20hit%20from%20hurricanes%20Helene%20and%20Milton%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20report%20will%20tell%20us%20little%20about%20the%20economy's%20trend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20headline%20number%20for%20October%20isn't%20the%20only%20part%20of%20the%20report%20that%20could%20reset%20expectations%2C%20however.%20According%20to%20Renaissance%20Macro%20Research%20Chief%20Economist%20Neil%20Dutta%2C%20there%20is%20some%20evidence%20that%20September's%20254%2C000%20jobs%20added%20could%20be%20creating%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20response%20rates%20to%20the%20BLS%20payrolls%20survey%20have%20been%20extraordinarily%20low%20this%20year%2C%20meaning%20revisions%20in%20subsequent%20months%20have%20been%20larger%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bls%20jobs%20report%20response%20rate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6721646201ea6d83dee4fa4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERenaissance%20Macro%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20there's%20no%20guaranteeing%20what%20will%20happen%20with%20September's%20data%2C%2075%25%20of%20revisions%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20have%20been%20negative%2C%20according%20to%20economist%20David%20Rosenberg.%20Rosenberg%20said%20in%20an%20October%209%20note%20that%20ADP's%20payrolls%20report%20is%20a%20more%20reliable%20survey%20to%20follow%2C%20and%20the%20firm's%20estimate%20of%20jobs%20added%20in%20September%20was%20143%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20sign%20that%20September's%20jobs%20numbers%20may%20have%20been%20overstat