0Mr%20Kejriwal's%20baseless%20statements%20but%20was%20forced%20to%20do%20so%20this%20time%20because%20it%20concerned%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%2C%20which%20benefits%20crores%20of%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20kept%20lakhs%20of%20people%20of%20Delhi%20deprived%20of%20this%20scheme%20till%20now%20only%20because%20of%20the%20fear%20that%20its%20implementation%20may%20reveal%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20false%20health%20model%20being%20promoted%20by%20you%20and%20your%20habit%20of%20taking%20false%20credit%20for%20everything%20may%20get%20exposed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20opposed%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20because%20he%20wanted%20his%20name%20associated%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20criticised%20the%20Delhi%20and%20West%20Bengal%20governments%20for%20failing%20to%20implement%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20health%20insurance%20scheme%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20interests%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%20had%20accused%20the%20PM%20of%20indulging%20in%20politics%20over%20public%20health.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20had%20also%20questioned%20the%20benefits%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20saying%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20had%20found%20several%20irregularities%2C%20and%20claimed%20a%20similar%20initiative%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20had%20benefited%20lakhs%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20scathing%20attack%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20health%20department%20had%20recommended%20implementing%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20in%20June%202018%20and%20the%20then%20health%20minister%20had%20given%20permission%20for%20doing%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20in%20August%202018%2C%20your%20government%20talked%20about%20naming%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20'Chief%20Minister%20Aa