ts%20of%20it%20being%20a%20suspected%20cause%20of%20food%20poisoning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Terrorist%26quot%3B%3A%20Nawab%20Malik%20Slams%20BJP%20Leader's%20%26quot%3BIrresponsible%26quot%3B%20Comment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENawab%20Malik%2C%20now%20the%20official%20candidate%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20the%20allegations%20now%20levelled%20at%20him%20were%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20verdicts%20in%20the%20cases%20would%20vindicate%20him.%20His%20response%20was%20to%20the%20remarks%20of%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Kirit%20Somaiya%2C%20who%20had%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20irresponsible%20statements.%20Nawab%20Malik%20was%20never%20a%20terrorist%20nor%20was%20ever%20with%20any%20terrorist%20or%20any%20criminal.%20Nawab%20Malik%20has%20been%20in%20politics%20in%20this%20country%20for%2050%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Malik%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20think%20giving%20such%20comments%20would%20help%20increase%20their%20vote%20bank%20but%20it%20actually%20has%20the%20opposite%20effect%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20matter%20is%20sub%20judice%2C%20so%20I%20can't%20obviously%20discuss%20it.%20Once%20the%20verdict%20comes%2C%20everything%20will%20be%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malik%20was%20arrested%20by%20central%20agencies%20in%20an%20alleged%20%C2%A0money%20laundering%20case%20involving%20mafia%20don%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20and%20his%20associates%20Chhota%20Shakeel%20and%20Tigar%20Memon.%20He%20is%20currently%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20refused%20to%20support%20his%20candidature%2C%20citing%20the%20case%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20won't%20endorse%20anyone%20who's%20related%20to%20any%20Dawood%20or%20Dawood%20related%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20had%20said%20yesterday%2C%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20last-minute%20backing%20fr%20Mr%20Malik%2C%20he%20said%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20campaign%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNawab%20Malik%20is%20a%20terrorist%20who%20tried%20to%20break%20India%20into%20pieces.%20He%20is%20Dawood's%20agent%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20has%20betrayed%20the%20country%20by%20giving%20ticket%20to%20Nawab%20Malik%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirit%20Somaiyya%20later%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malik%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20two%20nominations%20yesterday%20-%20one%20of%20them%20as%20an%20Independent%20and%20the%20other%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20to%20day%20said%20he%20ws%20not%20keen%20on%20contesting%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20a%205-term%20MLA%20and%20have%20been%20a%20minister%206%20times.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20contest%20the%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20he%20changed%20his%20mind%20because%20of%20appeals%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Mankhurd%20Shivaji%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730305380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fa8tifgc_nawab-malik-_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-a-terrorist-nawab-malik-slams-bjp-leaders-irresponsible-comment-6910221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nawab%20Malik%2C%20now%20the%20official%20candidate%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20the%20allegations%20now%20levelled%20at%20him%20were%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20verdicts%20in%20the%20cases%20would%20vindicate%20him%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%