%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5jrrcslg_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'MINDFULNESS%20CITY'%20-%20BUT%20WHY%20IN%20GELEPHU%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20in%20Gelephu%20is%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20and%20pristine%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20Butanese%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20region%20is%20a%20biological%20hot%20spot%2C%20with%20abundant%20potential%20for%20clean%20energy%2C%20but%20why%20this%20mega%20project%20here%3F%20he%20had%20asked%20the%20King%2C%20wondering%20why%20such%20a%20project%20was%20not%20being%20considered%20for%20Thimphu%20or%20Paro%20-%20where%20there%20is%20ready%20infrastructure%2C%20like%20airports%2C%20highways%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fdlmm697s_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20King%20had%20a%20one-word%20reply%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20-%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B.%20He%20then%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3BOur%20future%20is%20linked%20with%20India.%20If%20we%20chose%20any%20other%20place%2C%20then%20such%20a%20project%20may%20succeed%2C%20it%20may%20have%20its%20challenges%2C%20but%20if%20we%20plan%20this%20along%20the%20border%20with%20India%2C%20the%20concept%20itself%20will%20drive%20it%20to%20success%2C%20because%20Bhutan's%20future%20is%20intrinsically%20linked%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20recalled%20the%20King%20having%20said%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20t