n%20the%20reason%20for%20Kirsten's%20sudden%20resignation%2C%20sources%20have%20confirmed%20that%20it%20was%20because%20he%20was%20not%20involved%20when%20the%20Board%20announced%20the%20squads%20for%20the%20Australia%20and%20Zimbabwe%20tours%20and%20the%20new%20captain%20of%20the%20white%20ball%20format%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPCB%20sources%2C%20on%20their%20part%2C%20claimed%20that%20Kirsten%20had%20breached%20some%20clauses%20of%20his%20contract%2C%20notably%20by%20not%20spending%20enough%20time%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20insisting%20on%20having%20a%20full%20foreign%20coaching%20support%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20said%20that%20the%20PCB%20had%20started%20the%20process%20of%20finding%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20white%20ball%20team%20and%20he%20had%20already%20spoken%20to%20some%204-5%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20have%20a%20new%20white%20ball%20head%20coach%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%20because%20Jason%20Gillispie%20has%20only%20agreed%20to%20manage%20the%20team%20in%20Australia%20for%20the%20white%20ball%20matches%20on%20an%20interim%20basis.%20He%20is%20more%20focussed%20on%20his%20role%20as%20red%20ball%20head%20coach%2C%26quot%3B%20Naqvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20will%20have%20a%20new%20white%20ball%20coach%20for%20the%20Zimbabwe%20tour.%26quot%3B%20Insiders%20say%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aaqib%20Javed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F39944-aaqib-javed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAaqib%20Javed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20selector%20who%20Naqvi%20wanted%20to%20take%20over%20as%20Kirsten's%20replacement%2C%20has%20said%20he%20is%20more%20interested%20in%20working%20on%20development%20of%20players%20and%20grooming%20of%20young%20talent%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20selectors%20had%20the%20authority%20to%20decide%20on%20whether%20to%20pick%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Fakhar%20Za