%20not%20perform%20an%20Islamic%20prayer%20or%20recite%20the%20Quran.%20The%20Taliban%20have%20also%20forbid%20female%20healthcare%20workers%20from%20meeting%20with%20their%20patients's%20male%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20women%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20call%20takbir%20or%20athan%20%5Bthe%20Islamic%20call%20to%20prayer%5D%2C%20they%20certainly%20cannot%20sing%20songs%20or%20music%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20remarks%20reported%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafghanistan-taliban-introduces-law-banning-media-publishing-of-living-beings-6786650%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Taliban%20Introduces%20Law%20Banning%20Media%20Publishing%20Images%20Of%20Living%20Things%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20an%20adult%20female%20prays%20and%20another%20female%20passes%20by%2C%20she%20must%20not%20pray%20loudly%20enough%20for%20them%20to%20hear...%20How%20could%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20sing%20if%20they%20aren't%20even%20permitted%20to%20hear%20each%20other's%20voices%20while%20praying%2C%20let%20alone%20for%20anything%20else%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hanafi%20was%20also%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2024%2F10%2F28%2Ftaliban-bans-women-from-hearing-each-others-voices%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman's%20voice%20is%20considered%20awrah%2C%20meaning%20that%20which%20must%20be%20covered%20and%20shouldn't%20be%20heard%20in%20public%2C%20even%20by%20other%20women%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20this%20year%2C%20Afghanistan's%20Taliban%20morality%20ministry%20pledged%20to%20implement%20a%20law%20banning%20news%20media%20from%20publishing%20images%20of%20all%20living%20things%2C%20with%20journalists%20told%20the%20rule%20will%20be%20gradually%20enforced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20after%20the%20Taliban%20government%20recently%20announced%20legislation%20formalising%20their%20strict%20interpretations%20of%20Islamic%20law%20that%20have%20been%20imposed%20since%20they%20swept%20to%20power%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730297040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fgka6db5_afghanistan-women_625x300_30_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftaliban-bans-afghan-women-from-hearing-each-other-report-6908631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Taliban%20in%20Afghanistan%20have%20imposed%20a%20new%2C%20oppressive%20rule%20that%20silences%20women's%20voices%20even%20further.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftaliban-bans-afghan-women-from-hearing-each-other-report-6908631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ghatkopar%20MLA's%20Assets%20Up%20575%25%2C%20Now%20He's%20Maharashtra's%20Richest%20Candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAround%208000%20candidates%20have%20filed%20nominations%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20wealthiest%20of%20them%20is%20the%20BJP's%20%C2%A0Parag%20Shah%20-%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20Ghatkopar%20East%20%C2%A0--%20whose%20current%20worth%20is%20is%20Rs%203383.06%20crore%20according%20to%20his%20election%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%20property%20has%20increased%20by%20575%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20last%205%20years.%20In%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20had%20mentioned%20his%20assets%20value%20as%20Rs%20550.62%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20an%20honest%20candidate.%20Even%20my%20enemies%20have%20never%20claimed%20that%20I%20am%20not%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20told%20NDTV%20today%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20man's%20wealth%20is%20not%20his%20property%20but%20his%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%20%26quot%3B