%20two%20countries.%20I%20hope%20that%2C%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20this%20consensus%2C%20our%20relations%20will%20be%20moving%20forward%20smoothly%20in%20the%20future%20and%20they%20will%20not%20be%20restricted%20or%20interrupted%20by%20specific%20disagreements%20between%20our%20two%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20some%20differences%20between%20neighbouring%20countries%20are%20natural%2C%20the%20ambassador%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20how%20to%20handle%20and%20solve%20them.%20The%20meeting%20of%20the%20two%20leaders%20has%20set%20a%20very%20good%20example%20for%20us%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20these%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20when%20direct%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20-%20which%20had%20been%20halted%20in%202020%20-%20would%20resume%2C%20the%20ambassador%20elicited%20laughter%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20looking%20forward%20to%20direct%20flights%20so%20I%20can%20fly%20back%20to%20Beijing%20directly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Feihong%20added%20that%20direct%20flights%20would%20be%20convenient%20for%20everybody%20and%20would%20save%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20trade%20ties%2C%20the%20ambassador%20also%20said%20he%20wants%20smooth%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20China%20in%20business%2C%20education%2C%20science%20and%20%26quot%3Bevery%20field%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Disengagement%20In%202%20Areas%20Complete'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Feihong's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20sources%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20said%20the%20disengagement%20in%20the%20two%20areas%20has%20been%20completed%20and%20patrolling%20would%20begin%20soon.%20The%20modalities%20for%20the%20patrolling%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20by%20ground%20commanders%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20sweets%20would%20be%20exchanged%20with%20Chinese%2