0For%20Projects%20In%20Bhutan's%20'Mindfulness%20City'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%20is%20among%20those%20in%20discussions%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20Bhutan's%20new%20'Gelephu%20Mindfulness%20City'%20as%20the%20tiny%20Himalayan%20kingdom%20seeks%20investment%20to%20build%20a%20mega%20township%20along%20its%20southern%20border%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%2C%20controlled%20by%20Asia's%20second-richest%20person%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20business%20houses%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20highest%20levels%26quot%3B%20to%20set%20up%20solar%20and%20hydroelectric%20plants%20in%20Bhutan's%201%2C000-square-kilometer%20(386%20square%20miles)%20flatlands%20where%20the%20new%20city%20is%20being%20built%2C%20Lotay%20Tshering%2C%20Gelephu's%20newly-appointed%20governor%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20mountainous%20country%20has%20a%20population%20of%20less%20than%20800%2C000%2C%20its%20mission%20to%20revamp%20its%20infrastructure%20creates%20another%20opportunity%20for%20the%20ports-to-power%20conglomerate%20that%20has%20been%20investing%20billions%20in%20its%20green%20energy%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutan%20has%20been%20a%20strategic%20and%20long-time%20ally%20for%20India%2C%20which%20is%20keen%20to%20curb%20China's%20influence%20in%20its%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foray%2C%20if%20it%20materializes%2C%20fits%20with%20the%20broader%20strategy%20of%20Adani's%20sprawling%20empire%20of%20expanding%20its%20international%20footprint.%20The%20Indian%20conglomerate%20is%20already%20developing%20infrastructure%20projects%20or%20vying%20for%20them%20in%20Israel%2C%20Kenya%2C%20Tanzania%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20sites%20have%20been%20identified%20for%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20that%20are%20expected%20to%20add%2020%20gigawatts%20in%20capacity%2C%20said%20Tshe