20By%20LSG%20But%20India%20Star%20Rejected%20It%20Due%20To...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20big%20names%2C%20that%20several%20reports%20have%20claimed%20will%20not%20be%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20retention%20list%20-%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20senior%20India%20player.%20KL%20Rahul%20is%20not%20only%20a%20wicketkeeper-batter%20but%20was%20also%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20seasons.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Rahul%20has%20led%20Punjab%20Kings%20also.%20While%20his%20form%20in%20international%20cricket%20has%20dwindled%20a%20bit%2C%20KL%20rahul%20remains%20a%20great%20asset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fkl-rahul-decided-to-move-on-from-lsg-due-to-professional-and-personal-reasons-source%2Farticleshow%2F114770767.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rahul%20was%20offered%20the%20top%20retention%20by%20LSG%20but%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20on%20for%20two%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLSG%20were%20ready%20to%20offer%20top%20retention%20bracket%20to%20Rahul%2C%20but%20Rahul%20eventually%20decided%20to%20move%20on%20due%20to%20personal%20and%20professional%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20there%20are%20four%20franchises%20who%20have%20expressed%20their%20interest%20in%20him%20-%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20and%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%20Expect%20all%20four%20to%20go%20hard%20for%20him%20in%20the%20auction%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20IPL%20retention%20guidelines%20released%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20auction%2C%20a%20team%20will%20lose%20Rs%2018%20crore%20from%20the%20increased%20purse%20of%20Rs%20120%20crore%20for%20the%20first%20player%20retained%2C%20Rs%2014%20crore%20for%20second%2C%20Rs%2011%20for%20third%20while%20for%20the%20uncapped%20players%2C%20a%20team%20will%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20Rs%204%20crore%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20team%20retains%20five%20capped%20players%2C%20they%20will%20lose%20Rs%2075%20crore%20from%20the%20auction%20pot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mega%20auction%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20overseas%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20November.%20The%20auction%20purse%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20Rs%20120%20crore%20from%20the%20Rs%20100%20crore%20teams%20had%20at%20their%20disposal%20at%20last%20year's%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20salary%20cap%20now%20comprises%20an%20auction%20purse%2C%20incremental%20performance%20pay%20and%20match%20fees.%20The%20match%20fee%2C%20set%20at%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20per%20game%2C%20has%20been%20introduced%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%20can%20retain%20up%20to%20six%20players%2C%20via%20retention%20or%20right%20to%20match%2C%20from%20the%20existing%20squad%2C%20the%20highest%20in%20IPL%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730287440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftmi3j3go_kl-rahul-sanjiv-goenka_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fkl-rahul-offered-top-retention-by-lsg-but-india-star-rejected-it-for-these-reasons-4-teams-in-race-to-rope-him-6908081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rahul%20was%20offered%20the%20top%20retention%20by%20LSG%20but%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20on%20for%20two%20reasons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fkl-rahul-offered-top-retention-b