on-1730190877.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C100%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372840%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20food.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20educate%20and%20empower%20consumers.%E2%80%9D-%20Dr%20Aman%20Basheer%20Sheikh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%20Initially%2C%20the%20team%20envisioned%20sourcing%20data%20from%20existing%20databases%20but%20soon%20discovered%20a%20lack%20of%20centralised%20repositories%20for%20product%20information%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20database%2C%20but%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20information%20on%20the%20internet%20was%20often%20inaccurate%20or%20outdated.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20attempting%20to%20scrape%20data%20for%20over%2050%2C000%20products%2C%20they%20opted%20for%20a%20meticulous%2C%20ground-up%20approach%20to%20ensure%20accuracy.%20Currently%2C%20the%20team%20sends%20photographers%20to%20supermarkets%20to%20capture%20product%20images%20and%20ingredient%20labels%20directly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20rely%20on%20internet%20data%20for%20about%2020%25%20of%20our%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20clarifies.%20Essentially%2C%20they%20crowdsource%20product%20images%20and%20information%20to%20verify%20product%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECombating%20misleading%20labels%C2%A0%3C%2F