E2%80%99t%20realise%20or%20understand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20the%20team%20remains%20committed%20to%20their%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20approach%20this%20from%20a%20solution-based%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20food.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20educate%20and%20empower%20consumers.%E2%80%9D%20The%20TruthIn%20team%20consists%20of%2035%20members%2C%20including%2015%20nutritionists%20and%20doctors%2C%20working%20alongside%20tech%20professionals.%20The%20initiative%20is%20entirely%20bootstrapped%20and%20self-funded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20TruthIn%20has%20an%20active%20user%20base%20of%20approximately%2085%2C000%20to%201%2C00%2C000%20users%20each%20month.%20The%20app%20features%20a%20unique%20TruthIn%20Rating%20system%20that%20assigns%20health%20impact%20of%20food%20products.%20Products%20are%20assigned%20health%20ratings%20on%20a%20scale%20from%201%20to%205%2C%20with%205%20being%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20Users%20can%20easily%20find%20products%20that%20match%20their%20dietary%20needs%20and%20preferences%20through%20filter%20tags%20for%20nutrients%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20allergens.%20The%20Shopping%20Cart%20Insights%20makes%20the%20shopping%20experience%20better%20by%20giving%20intelligent%20insights%20on%20cart%20contents%2C%20ensuring%20all%20products%20meet%20health%20criteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20simply%20scanning%20the%20barcode%20on%20a%20product%E2%80%99s%20packaging%2C%20users%20can%20get%20detailed%20information%20about%20its%20rating%20and%20relevant%20tags%2C%20such%20as%20high%20sodi