youth%2C%20particularly%20Gen%20Z.%20We%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20young%20people%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20who%20are%20feeling%20lonely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20began%20with%20a%20roadshow%2C%20travelling%20to%20150%20campuses%20in%2035%20cities%20over%20nine%20months.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20to%20talk%20about%20mental%20health%20and%20sexual%20health%2C%20providing%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20young%20people%20to%20share%20their%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20roadshow%2C%20Nikhil%20encountered%20many%20young%20boys%20whose%20stories%20moved%20him%20deeply.%20%E2%80%9CAn%2018-year-old%20boy%20told%20me%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20told%20him%20%E2%80%98I%20love%20you.%E2%80%99%20Another%20teen%20shared%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20hugged%20him.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20intimacy%20to%20our%20boys%20and%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eokay%20to%20express%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20space%20to%20all%20the%20boys%20and%20girls%20in%20our%20country%20by%20creating%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Nikhil%20started%20a%20show%20called%20%3Cem%3EBe%20a%20Man%2C%20Yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20male%20celebrities%20such%20as%20Javed%20Akhtar%2C%20Gajraj%20Rao%2C%20Boman%20Irani%2C%20Vicky%20Kaushal%2C%20Karan%20Johar%2C%20Bhuvan%20Bam%2C%20and%20Zakir%20Khan.%20The%20show%20promotes%20honest%2C%20vulnerable%20conversations%20where%20men%20talk%20about%20their%20feelings%20and%20mental%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzT1CUdo1-B%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_c